    ## Attributes
    {% include "src/templates/partials/jsProps.njk" %}
    
    | Attribute            | Type    | Validation                                                                                    | Default  | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
    | -------------------- | ------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
    | `eds-disable-border` | boolean | Anything other than empty string, `false`, or `eds-disable-border` will be treated as `true`. | `false`  | Disables the top border.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
    | `eds-inline`         | string  | `always`,`never`, `at-512`, `at-768`, `at-960`, `at-1280`                                              | `at-512` | Determines the point at which the content within the Form Actions goes from stacked to inline. For any breakpoint, if `eds-inline` is set to `never` the content within the Form Actions will stay stacked while `always` will force the content to stay inline. |
    | `eds-text`           | string  | --                                                                                            | --       | Text above the actions. Alternative to using the `text` slot.                                                                                                                                                                                                    |

    ## Slots
    | Name               | Default content | Description                                                                                                                                            |
    | ------------------ | --------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
    | `text`             | --              | Optional slot and alternative to `eds-text`. If you need HTML markup in the text above the actions section in Form Actions (e.g., links).               |
    | `primary-action`   | --              | Required slot for the "primary" action of your Form Actions. Use the "primary" variant of the `eds-button`.                                                |
    | `secondary-action` | --              | Optional slot for "secondary" actions of your Form Actions. Use the "secondary" variant of the `eds-button`.                                               |
    | `tertiary-action`  | --              | Optional slot for the "tertiary" action of your Form Actions.                                                                                            |

